quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  27,89,Iwo amene achita zabwino adzalandira mphotho imene ili yabwino ndipo adzakhala osakhudzidwa ndi zochititsa mantha za tsiku limeneli
  27,90,Koma iwo amene achita zoipa adzaduduluzidwa pa mphumi zawo kunka ku moto. “Kodi inu simudzalandira malipiro ofanana ndi ntchito zanu?”
  27,91,"Nena, “Ine ndalamulidwa kutumikira Ambuye wa mzinda uno umene waupanga kuti ukhale Woyera. Zinthu zonse ndi zake. Ndipo ndalamulidwa kukhala mmodzi mwa odzipereka.”"
  27,92,Ndipo ndalamulidwa kuwerenga Buku la Korani. Aliyense amene atsatira njira yoyenera atero podzithandiza yekha. Kwa iye amene asochera nena “Ine si ndine kanthu kena koma mmodzi wa iwo ochenjeza anthu.”
  27,93,"Ndipo nena, “Kuyamikidwa kukhale kwa Mulungu! Iye adzakulangizani zizindikiro zake ndipo inu mudzazizindikira. Ambuye wanu saiwala zimene mumachita.”"
  28,1,Ta Sin Mim
  28,2,Awa ndi mawu a m’Buku lofotokoza bwino
  28,3,Tidzakuuza zina za mbiri ya Mose ndi Farawo mwachoonadi kuti uuze anthu okhulupirira
  28,4,Ndithudi Farawo adadzikweza pa dziko lapansi ndipo adagawa anthu ake m’magulumagulu ndipo gulu lina iye anali kulizunza pomapha ana awo aamuna ndi kusiya ana aakazi. Ndithudi iye adali wochita zoipa
  28,5,Koma chidali chifuniro chathu kuti tiwapatse zabwino anthu amene adali oponderezedwa pa dziko ndi kuwasandutsa iwo kukhala atsogoleri a anthu ndi kuwapanga iwo kulowa m’malo mwa ufumu wa Farawo